docs {
  ## List Physical Count Detail Comments
  แสดงความคิดเห็นทั้งหมดของรายละเอียดการนับสินค้าจริง
  
  Retrieves all comments for a physical-count-detail.
  
  ### Path Parameters
  - `physical_count_detail_id` — Physical Count Detail ID
  
  
  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "uuid",
        "message": "comment text"
      }
    ],
    "paginate": {
      "total": 100,
      "page": 1,
      "perpage": 10,
      "pages": 10
    },
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}
